title: BUYBACK: How many Tokens?
body:
How many tokens do you think we should spend in the buyback mechanism?

Tokens will be send to buyback address, and a smart contract owner of this address will implement the buyback mechanism.

Note: the more tokens the buyback address has, the more tokens it will receive per reflection in each transaction.
author: 0x05078E63d080c292478504Df1170289B23E9659B
